, decoupled HSTN. We\nalso outline open issues to envision an agile, smart, and secure HSTN for the\nsixth-generation (6G) ubiquitous Internet of Things (IoT).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2020 04:10:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 7 Feb 2021 09:33:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-09"}
